    <h2>Benefits</h2>

<p>You get 50% off:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Adult pay as you go bus and tram fares</li>
	<li>Adult 7 Day or monthly (up to six months) <a href="/fares/how-to-pay-and-where-to-buy-tickets-and-oyster/bus-and-tram-pass">Bus &amp; Tram Passes</a></li>
</ul>

<h2>Can I get it?</h2>

<p>You must be:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Living in a <a href="https://directory.londoncouncils.gov.uk/">London borough</a></li>
	<li>Aged between 18 and 60</li>
	<li>Getting no other free or discounted travel</li>
</ul>

<p>And, claiming <strong>one</strong> of these benefits:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Income Support or Employment and Support Allowance</li>
	<li>Jobseekers Allowance for at least 13 weeks</li>
	<li>Universal Credit for at least 13 weeks, and not earning more than the threshold defined by the Department for Work and Pensions</li>
</ul>

<h2>How to apply</h2>

<ol>
	<li>Print off an application form, or get one from some London Post Offices and London Jobcentre Plus offices</li>
</ol> 
</div>
 
